rows.label: qst710502_msg0003
rows.name:
You've actually defeated every
last one of the unique monsters
in Gula and Iira?

rows.label: qst710502_msg0005
rows.name:
To tell you the truth, I never really
thought it would happen in my lifetime.

rows.label: qst710502_msg0006
rows.name:
I thought for sure I was going to have
to ask my grandchildren to finish the
job for me. I'm stunned.

rows.label: qst710502_msg0007
rows.name:
I finally have everything I need to
complete my Comprehensive Guide
to the Unique Monsters of Alst.

rows.label: qst710502_msg0008
rows.name:
I'm sure this will become a valuable
resource a few centuries down the line.

rows.label: qst710502_msg0009
rows.name:
Thank you all so much. You've made
an old woman's dream come true.
